{"tid":2247820,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分開咗三個月喇","createTime":"2020-10-18T06:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T11:43:10.000Z","uid":344869,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"78f7fb53a9b0b4b851e517919fc035304b268d33","tid":2247820,"uid":344869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T06:57:24.000Z","msg":"仲係唔捨得你<br />\n仲係以為今次講分手 我氹 你就返嚟<br />\n你近況點完全唔知道 （好彩有follow你而家啲同學間唔中都見到有你喺度）亦都好好奇但係冇身份去過問<br />\n覺得除咗失去咗個女朋友之外 自己好似冇咗個了解我嘅人同可以傾心事嘅人 依家開心唔知係邊個分享唔開心又唔知可以搵邊個訴苦 <br />\n你而家大學生活應該都過得多姿多彩 唔知搵到男朋友未呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同你一齊雖然唔耐 但有好多經歷 第一次都係你比我<br />\n可能亦都係我第一次投入感情去愛一個人 真係好掛住你"},{"pid":"b707ed6931aa18672cdc827d9f2d56873b76beff","tid":2247820,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T06:58:55.000Z","msg":"樓主加油撐過去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb39e6a5316b0ce2cd084926bda27d91fb1ae166","tid":2247820,"uid":243351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T07:00:41.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"e377429135eabfb3cd1062cf0d8e94ba4f40ab66","tid":2247820,"uid":5883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T07:01:45.000Z","msg":"經歷緊一模一樣既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67244f2f3db8e9a727e1f9df27fc903f4ae78e6","tid":2247820,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e377429135eabfb3cd1062cf0d8e94ba4f40ab66","tid":2247820,"uid":5883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T07:01:45.000Z","msg":"經歷緊一模一樣既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T07:03:14.000Z","msg":"大家加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22037ba37abbdc1b427cbe8fdc62c078a59de989","tid":2247820,"uid":5883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f67244f2f3db8e9a727e1f9df27fc903f4ae78e6","tid":2247820,"uid":3